      "createdAt": "2024-01-26T05:35:11.201Z",
      "author": "Valeriia.H (Valeriia)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hi <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/eashley06\">@Eashley06</a>! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/wave.png?v=12\" title=\":wave:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":wave:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>Try <a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/10000106?utm_source=Monday&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=Comment_display-ooo-status-on-calendar_20240125\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Time in Status </a>app which track time the Item has spent in each workflow status. So you can monitor how fast the Item moves between statuses.<br />\nYou’ll get user-friendly data on the board in a few seconds.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/b/9/b9fa33072428815ef1af97bdf9d6b7464a40008f.jpeg\" title=\"Знімок екрана 2024-01-26 о 03.33.48\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/b/9/b9fa33072428815ef1af97bdf9d6b7464a40008f_2_690x175.jpeg\" alt=\"Знімок екрана 2024-01-26 о 03.33.48\" width=\"690\" height=\"175\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Знімок екрана 2024-01-26 о 03.33.48</span><span class=\"informations\">1920×488 50.2 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Also you will be able to track how much time your issue spends in each status and much more by generating 3 types of reports:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://saasjet.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SAASJET/pages/2795503882\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><strong>Time in Status Report</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://saasjet.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SAASJET/pages/2795503937\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><strong>Status Count Report</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://saasjet.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SAASJET/pages/2795503992/Transition+Count+Report.\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><strong>Transition Count Report</strong></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/chart_with_upwards_trend.png?v=12\" title=\":chart_with_upwards_trend:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":chart_with_upwards_trend:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> And use <a href=\"https://saasjet.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SAASJET/pages/2795504246\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><strong>charts</strong></a> to visualize your reports a sample of a certain number according to time range/item range, or a <a href=\"https://saasjet.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SAASJET/pages/2795504311\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><strong>single</strong> </a><strong>item</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Pie Charts</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Bar Charts</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Area Charts</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p>The app is also available in the format of board integration.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/e/7/e7392b1cf0f1d5828cc0b51ef89ca6a1de85d676.jpeg\" title=\"Знімок екрана 2024-01-26 о 03.35.01\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/e/7/e7392b1cf0f1d5828cc0b51ef89ca6a1de85d676_2_690x284.jpeg\" alt=\"Знімок екрана 2024-01-26 о 03.35.01\" width=\"690\" height=\"284\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Знімок екрана 2024-01-26 о 03.35.01</span><span class=\"informations\">1538×634 95.8 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>You can try it on the <a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/10000106?utm_source=Monday&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=Comment_display-ooo-status-on-calendar_20240125\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday Marketplace </a>and share your experience with us.<br />\nHope you find this app helpful.</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": 245050,
      "postNumber": 3,
      "createdAt": "2026-01-29T11:20:17.133Z",
      "author": "byteboutiquein (Raj)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>We built an <strong>Out of Office Assistant</strong> for monday that handles OOO coverage automatically.</p>\n<p><strong>What it does</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Each user sets their OOO dates + backup once (Global setting)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>On boards you choose: when the owner is OOO, the app <strong>posts a clear update</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Optional <strong>auto-reassign to the backup</strong> (Hard mode)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>If the backup isn’t a board subscriber (private board), it <strong>won’t reassign</strong>—it will only notify in updates</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Optional <strong><span class=\"mention\">@mention</span> auto-reply</strong> with rate-limiting</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Marketplace link: <a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/listing/10001034/out-of-office-assistant\" class=\"inline-onebox\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Out Of Office Assistant - monday.com Marketplace</a></p>"
    },
