      "author": "byteboutiquein (Raj)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hi <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/eashley06\">@Eashley06</a></p>\n<p>We built <strong>Out of Office Assistant</strong> to solve it inside boards:<br />\n• Users set OOO dates + choose a backup (global)<br />\n• Admin picks board behavior: <strong>Warn</strong> or <strong>Auto-reassign to backup</strong><br />\n• <strong><span class=\"mention\">@mention</span> auto-reply</strong> with rate limits to avoid spam</p>\n<aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/d/d/dd4cf2ca4142e9b9bbb7fb50954ca95b2c203dfa.png\" class=\"site-icon\" alt=\"\" width=\"256\" height=\"256\" />\n\n      <a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/listing/10001034/out-of-office-assistant\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    \n\n<h3><a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/listing/10001034/out-of-office-assistant\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Out Of Office Assistant - monday.com Marketplace</a></h3>\n\n  <p>Automatically route work when users are out of office.</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div></div>\n</aside>\n\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/2/0/207d4136e5da98497cfa0ccdba140f715d3be475.png\" title=\"Ticket\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/2/0/207d4136e5da98497cfa0ccdba140f715d3be475_2_690x374.png\" alt=\"Ticket\" width=\"690\" height=\"374\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Ticket</span><span class=\"informations\">2940×1594 344 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/b/3/b330fe3df2679a23bd7d3001453d443d27053704.png\" title=\"ooo\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/b/3/b330fe3df2679a23bd7d3001453d443d27053704_2_690x410.png\" alt=\"ooo\" width=\"690\" height=\"410\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">ooo</span><span class=\"informations\">2402×1430 362 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/b/3/b3f766ab222efee5f3424a747da3f5356be8e5ff.jpeg\" title=\"Board_Rules\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/b/3/b3f766ab222efee5f3424a747da3f5356be8e5ff_2_459x500.jpeg\" alt=\"Board_Rules\" width=\"459\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Board_Rules</span><span class=\"informations\">1920×2091 260 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>"
